## Component Specifications

### Notation Badge
- Dark background (#1A1A1A), white text
- Monospace font, small padding (2px 6px)
- Minimal border-radius (2px)
- Variants: --sm, default, --lg

### Status Indicator
- Colored dot (8px) + uppercase label
- Dot color matches status
- Background: surface color

### Cards (Idea/Story/Sprint)
- Dense padding (12px)
- Left border (3px) indicates status color
- Title, description (clamped to 3 lines), meta footer
- Subtle hover state (border darkens, slight shadow)

### Navigation
- Fixed position, 48px height
- Logo + notation badge left, links center, search right
- Links: uppercase, small, letter-spaced

## Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Card Grid | Header | Kanban |
|------------|-----------|--------|--------|
| >1280px | 5 columns | 4/5 + 1/5 | 3 columns |
| 1024-1280px | 4 columns | 4/5 + 1/5 | 3 columns |
| 768-1024px | 3 columns | Stacked | Scrollable |
| 480-768px | 2 columns | Stacked | Tabs |
| <480px | 1 column | Stacked | Tabs |

## Anti-Patterns (Do NOT Do)

- ❌ Decorative colors or gradients
- ❌ Rounded corners > 4px
- ❌ Drop shadows for decoration
- ❌ Italic text (except citations)
- ❌ Centered body text
- ❌ Excessive whitespace between elements
- ❌ Icons without labels in navigation
- ❌ Low-contrast text
